      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "API\n\n// shorten a url\nPOST /urls -> shortul\n{\n    originalUrl,\n    alias?,\n    expirationTime?\n}\n\n// redirection\nGET {shortUrl} -> Redirect to OriginalUrl\n\n",
