      "index": "aI",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1573323122,
      "version": 937,
      "versionNonce": 2104346162,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1773731868919,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- fast\n- unique\n- short (5-7)\n\n1. prefix of long url\n2. random number generator 10^9 10 character\n    - base62 encoding, 0-9, A-Z, a-z\n    - 62^6 = 56B\n    - birthday paradox\n    - 880k collisions\n    - we check from databse collision first\n3. has the long url\n    - md5(longurl) -> hash -> base62(hash)[:6]\n4. counter\n    - incrementing a counter -> base62\n    - predictability which is bad for security\n        - warn don't shorten private urls\n        - rate limiting\n    - bijective function\n        - sqids.org",
      "fontSize": 14.026040039062499,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- fast\n- unique\n- short (5-7)\n\n1. prefix of long url\n2. random number generator 10^9 10 character\n    - base62 encoding, 0-9, A-Z, a-z\n    - 62^6 = 56B\n    - birthday paradox\n    - 880k collisions\n    - we check from databse collision first\n3. has the long url\n    - md5(longurl) -> hash -> base62(hash)[:6]\n4. counter\n    - incrementing a counter -> base62\n    - predictability which is bad for security\n        - warn don't shorten private urls\n        - rate limiting\n    - bijective function\n        - sqids.org",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
